<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<androidx.constraintlayout.widget.ConstraintLayout xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
    xmlns:app="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res-auto"
    xmlns:tools="http://schemas.android.com/tools"
    android:layout_width="match_parent"
    android:layout_height="match_parent"
    android:background="@drawable/bg3"
    android:visibility="visible"
    tools:context=".AboutUsInfo">


    <TextView
        android:id="@+id/textView"
        android:layout_width="300dp"
        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
        android:text="Welcome to immunity testing application!!!
As you are using immunity testing application, then of course
you will get an basic idea about how healthy you are or how healthy your
immune system is.In which you can check your percent of immunity or you will
get to what type of immunity you are having, if your immunity is low or high then
 what precautions you should take, if your immunity is very low then what care or
  diet you should follow, etc. this kind information you will get after solving a quiz.
   after answering every question from the quiz, you will get an instruction
    message which will show you the precautions and diet plan."
        android:textSize="18sp"
        android:textStyle="bold"
        app:fontFamily="sans-serif"
        app:layout_constraintBottom_toBottomOf="parent"
        app:layout_constraintEnd_toEndOf="parent"
        app:layout_constraintHorizontal_bias="0.495"
        app:layout_constraintStart_toStartOf="parent"
        app:layout_constraintTop_toTopOf="parent"
        app:layout_constraintVertical_bias="0.442" />

    <TextView
        android:id="@+id/textView3"
        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
        android:text="ABOUT US"
        android:textSize="30sp"
        android:textStyle="bold"
        app:fontFamily="serif"
        app:layout_constraintBottom_toTopOf="@+id/textView"
        app:layout_constraintEnd_toEndOf="parent"
        app:layout_constraintStart_toStartOf="parent"
        app:layout_constraintTop_toTopOf="parent"
        app:layout_constraintVertical_bias="0.533" />
</androidx.constraintlayout.widget.ConstraintLayout>